            <section>
               <id root="1c601154-7a5d-4716-ae9f-c531d90a7d64"/>
               <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
               <title>STORAGE</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Store at 20°-25°C (68°-77°F); excursions permitted to 15°-30°C (59°-86°F). See USP Controlled Room Temperature.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Dispense in a tight, light resistant container with a child-resistant closure as defined in the USP/NF. All prescription substitutions using this product shall be pursuant to state statutes as applicable. This is not an Orange Book product.
       
 
  <br/>
